title: Bedouin Burger - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Bedouin Burger performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded August 16, 2022.

Songs:
Ma Ajmalou
Nomad 
Harir
Taht El Ward 

Zeid Hamdan -  Guitar / Synth / Percussion / Vocals
Lynn Adib - Flute / Synth / Percussion / Vocals

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro & Scott Holpainen
Editor: Scott Holpainen
